<title>JAPAN: Okura up on millennium bug software demand.</title>
<headline>Okura up on millennium bug software demand.</headline>
<dateline>TOKYO 1997-08-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares of Okura &amp; Co Ltd surged on Friday afternoon due to the expectation that its software business would benefit from the so-called millennium bug problem.</p>
<p>The stock was the top percentage gainer on the Tokyo Stock Exchange's first section in the afternoon session.</p>
<p>Okura's shares were up 55 yen at 455 yen as of 0435 GMT.</p>
